    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-10-02T12:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-10-02T12:00:00-05:00" n="638"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d638">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.6359/10–248: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stuart</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1948-10-02T12:00:00-05:00"
                            >October 2, 1948—noon.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1390. Ref last para urtel 1818, Oct 2, you are authorized to conclude
                    understanding on basis Deptel 859, June 9, which is finalized position of Dept
                    with reference para 3, Deptel 783.<note n="22" xml:id="d638fn22">May 26, <ref
                            target="#pg_745">p. 745</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lovett</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
